<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Rosedale</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Rosedale is a short distance away from the Kensington Business Revitalization Zone, home to a variety of owner run shops and well-known Calgary restaurants, including the Broken Plate, a famous Greek restaurant. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The area is also home to the Plaza theatre, which hosts showings of classics, independent films and low-budget film festivals. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Rosedale Community Centre is home to the Calgary Ski Club, offering ski trips to members, as well as skiing lessons for people new to the sport. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community also operates public tennis courts. </p>

        </div>
